{"tid":2310743,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"郊遊一肚火！汪明荃用樹枝執口罩鬧爆：冇公德心","createTime":"2020-12-03T13:00:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-03T13:47:34.000Z","uid":16659,"like":10,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"68ffd5b1137fe4baca169bc94140d66fe2efe27a","tid":2310743,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T13:00:46.000Z","msg":"「阿姐」汪明荃最近趁住好天氣攞啲手袋同鞋出嚟曬吓太陽，心情鬼咁靚，尋日佢又出去行吓曬吓自己，點知竟然一肚火！原來佢見到好多垃圾，隨地都係口罩，搞到佢忍唔住用樹枝執起啲口罩，仲嬲爆鬧啲人冇公德心：「在清水灣郊野步行1小時，本來心情幾好，但見到隨地的垃圾，仍然忍唔住，用樹枝執起啲『口罩』，唉！有啲人真係冇公德心！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20201203/photo/bkn-20201203100923556-1203_00862_001_02p.jpg?20201203161408\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20201203%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20201203100923556-1203_00862_001_02p.jpg%3F20201203161408&h=31028f41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20201203/photo/bkn-20201203100923556-1203_00862_001_03p.jpg?20201203161408\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20201203%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20201203100923556-1203_00862_001_03p.jpg%3F20201203161408&h=b027ea66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔少網民都多謝佢，又留言「Liza 姐人美心善，辛苦晒👍👍👍，香港好多質素差的生物，自私自利極之討厭😡」、「完全感受到阿姐對香港滿滿嘅愛！！❤️😆👍出心出力」、「大家要向阿姐學習👏👏」！<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20201203/photo/bkn-20201203100923556-1203_00862_001_04p.jpg?20201203161408\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20201203%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20201203100923556-1203_00862_001_04p.jpg%3F20201203161408&h=813fdd11&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e4822529b4201c35982ff3912b6c8eea454339b1","tid":2310743,"uid":256796,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T13:01:59.000Z","msg":"樓主依家轉型 po啲70路<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50ca5548fc0a5292ca45f5285d6254d02ec05359","tid":231074